 //draws a container with padding around it. Can use container-fluid as well. Bootstrap grid also require the container inside of them
 
 <div class="page-header">
 //will include space between any of the text as well  as in-large any of the text inside of it. Also provides underline after the text is displayed.
 </div>
 
 <div class="jumbotron">
 //enlarge your fonts and place everything inside of great box by default with rounded corners. WE can change the color and background color of it. If used outside container will fill teh complete width
 //To make the jumbotron full width, and without rounded corners, add the .jumbotron-fluid modifier class and add a .container or .container-fluid within.
